This paper deals with the analysis of a data structure, specifically a variant of Fibonacci heaps. Therefore, the most likely category is cs.DS (Data Structures and Algorithms). The paper also involves probabilistic analysis, which suggests categories such as cs.DM (Discrete Mathematics) and cs.IT (Information Theory). Additionally, the paper involves runtime analysis, which could fall under categories such as cs.NA (Numerical Analysis) and cs.CC (Computational Complexity).
